Centralize color palette in app/styles/theme.ts; define semantic tokens (e.g., primary, secondary, background).

Use CSS variables for theme overrides; support light and dark modes with prefers-color-scheme media query.

Define font scale: base=16px, small=14px, large=20px, xlarge=24px; apply via utility classes.

Button radii: apply rounded-lg for primary, rounded-md for secondary.

Shadows: use shadow-sm for cards, shadow-md for modals, shadow-lg for overlays.

Maintain a spacing scale: use multiples of 0.25rem; avoid arbitrary margins or paddings.

Icons: use a shared icon library (e.g., lucide-react); standardize icon size to 1.5rem unless context demands otherwise.

Ensure color contrast ratios meet WCAG AA: check text and background pairings.

Animate transitions: use CSS transitions for hover states; keep duration under 200ms.


Store global styles in app/styles/global.css; avoid inline style overrides.